==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
*πρεσβυτέριον / presbuterion / pres-boo-ter'-ee-on
*Neuter of a presumed derivative of G4245; the order of elders, that is, (specifically) Israelite Sanhedrim or Christian “presbytery”: 

===Noun===
'''πρεσβυτέριον'''

# (estate of) elder (-s), [[presbytery]].

